        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Southern Border Communities Reimbursement Act of 2021 </b></p> <p>This bill authorizes reimbursement to jurisdictions and organizations for the costs of providing humanitarian relief to aliens, including the cost of emergency preparedness activities. The reimbursement authorized under this bill shall be for FY2021-FY2023 and shall be distributed by the Emergency Food and Shelter Program National Board.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
